fields.name: Gaia Red Velvet Dress
fields.description: Our iconic Gaia dress, now in a luscious high grade stretchy velvet fabric. It is Gaia but with even more glamour and elegance, it looks like pure wealth. Designed for every woman to embrace every curve and walk into the room with the utmost confidence.

fields.name: Blue Mesh Hydrodynamic Ruched Mini Dress
fields.material: Body: 80% polyamide, 20% viscose. Lining: 81% polyamide, 19% elastane.
fields.description: Long sleeve panelled semi-sheer viscose-blend mesh short dress in blue. Ruching throughout. Mock neck collar. Thumb opening at cuffs. Padding at side-seam. Zip closure at back. Full stretch mesh lining. Tonal hardware.

fields.name: Black Wool Flatground Skirt
fields.material: Body 1: 100% wool. Body 2: 61% polyamide, 39% acetate. Trim: 100% cotton. Lining: 61% polyamide, 39%
fields.description: Paneled wool gabardine and nylon-blend satin mid-length skirt in black. Mid-rise. Two-pocket styling. Belt loops at waistband. Partially concealed button closure at front. Central vent at front hem. Tonal logo-engraved hardware.

fields.name: Orange Campo Dress
fields.description: Cap sleeve organic cotton jersey mid-length dress in orange featuring graphic pattern in multicolor. Crewneck collar. Elasticized trim with gathering at front.

fields.name: Beige Powertulle Corset Dress
fields.description: Long sleeve semi-sheer stretch nylon tulle mid-length dress in beige. Paneled construction. Integrated boning throughout. Elasticized halter strap with toggle fastening at modified V-neck collar. Underwire at cups. Zip closure at back. Unlined. Silver-tone hardware.

fields.name: Beige Button-Down Open Back Dress
fields.description: Short sleeve faux-leather mid-length dress in beige. Spread collar. Button closure at front. Elasticized waistband. Faux-flap pockets at waist. Cut-out at back. Unlined.

fields.name: Beige Open Sleeve Blazer
fields.description: Long sleeve cotton and nylon-blend grosgrain blazer in beige. Y-neck collar. Double-breasted press-stud closure and cut-outs at front. Welt pockets at chest and waist. Padded shoulders. Cut-out at sleeves. Central vent at back hem. Viscose twill lining in grey. Fully lined.

fields.name: Beige & Pink Canvas Painted Coat
fields.description: Half sleeve cotton canvas coat in beige. Printed graphic in pink at front. Spread collar. Button closure at front. Flap pockets at chest and waist. Unlined. Tonal hardware.

fields.name: Grey Stripe Suiting Blazer
fields.material: Body: 54% recycled polyester, 44% virgin wool, 2% elastane. Lining: 100% polyester.
fields.description: Long sleeve woven stretch virgin wool-blend blazer in grey featuring striped pattern in tones of grey. Notched lapel collar. Two-button closure at front. Flap pockets and detachable belt-style strap with button and hook fastening at waist. Padded shoulders. Two-button barrel cuffs. Welt pocket at interior. Logo-woven satin lining in black. Fully lined. Black hardware.

fields.name: Orange & Tan Carl Leggings
fields.description: Stretch viscose jersey leggings colorblocked in tones of orange and tan. Graphic pattern in multicolor throughout. High-rise. Integrated belt-style strap with O-ring hardware at elasticized waistband. Pale gold-tone hardware.

fields.name: Beige Open Knee Trousers
fields.description: Tapered cotton and nylon-blend grosgrain trousers in beige. High-rise. Four-pocket styling. Belt loops at waistband. Pleats at front. Cut-out at knees. Rolled cuffs. Zip-fly.

fields.name: Black Faux-Leather Slouch Pants
fields.description: Relaxed-fit buffed faux-leather pants in black. Mid-rise. Four-pocket styling. Pinched seam at front legs. Zip-fly. Antiqued brass-tone hardware.

fields.name: Off-White Mass Box Pleated Skirt
fields.material: Made in United Kingdom.  211742F090012  Maximilian - Off-White Mass Box Pleated Skirt Maximilian -
fields.description: Plain-woven wool short skirt in off-white. Low-rise. Self-tie straps with bead accents at waist. Pleats at back waistband. Zip closure at side-seam. Full cupro satin lining. Tonal hardware.

fields.name: Pink Inside Out Trompe-l'œil T-Shirt
fields.description: Short sleeve cotton jersey T-shirt featuring graphic printed in white and tones of pink throughout. Rib knit crewneck collar. Grosgrain logo flag in black and white at back collar.

fields.name: Black Oscar Wilde Cropped Wide Sleeve Sweater
fields.description: Knit wool sweater in black. Jacquard knit floral pattern in multicolor throughout. Rib knit crewneck collar, cuffs, and hem. Grosgrain trim in grey featuring embroidered text in black at front. Dropped shoulders. Cropped hem.

fields.name: Orange All Over Print Crop Long Sleeve T-Shirt
fields.description: Long sleeve stretch cotton jersey T-shirt in orange featuring logo and text printed in black throughout. Rib knit crewneck collar. Cropped hem.

fields.name: Peephole Dress
fields.description: One size fits all

fields.name: Sailor T-Shirt
fields.description: xxx

fields.name: Zuwa Bubu Dress
fields.description: Zuwa is a bubu with a high slit and an elegant one-shoulder detail. If you love glamour but also comfort, you will love Zuwa. It is generously cut from the most gorgeous silky satin.

fields.name: Bea Dress Ginger
fields.description: The Bea dress in cotton is a beauty that can be worn for a summer wedding with killer heels or to the beach over a pair of shorts. Its range is amazing. It comes with a belt to cinch it in at the waist. You can do away with the belt and leave it open over a pair of jeans- it’s entirely up to you as it’s a stunner any which way you look at it.
